sentences: In its decision (FCCC/SBI/2010/L.24/Add.2), the COP/MOP, inter alia , urges parties to further contribute to the Trust Fund for Participation in the UNFCCC Process and the Trust Fund for Supplementary Activities.
Privileges and Immunities: This issue (FCCC/SBI/2010/10) was first considered in SBI plenary on 30 November.
The SBI agreed to continue consideration of this issue at SBI 34.
